text: Kozhay-Maximovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Beketovsky Selsoviet, Yermekeyevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 6 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 39 km from Yermekeyevo, 14 km from Beketovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yermekeyevsky District
title: Kozhay-Maximovo
